sourcesContent: import React,{useState} from 'react' import { Button,Modal } from 'react-bootstrap' function ResultData(student,percentage) { console.log(student.name) console.log(percentage) const [show, setShow] = useState(false); const handleClose = () => setShow(false); const handleShow = () => setShow(true); return ( <> {student.name} {student.registration_no} {percentage} Modal heading {percentage} ) } export default ResultData
